{"id":"helon","term":"Helon","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Strong, father of Eliab, who was “captain of the children of Zebulun” (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 1:9\">Num. 1:9</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 2:7\">2:7</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 1:9","Numbers 2:7"]}